'From Squeak2.8alpha of 4 February 2000 [latest update: #2005] on 22 April 2000 at 12:40:30 pm'!"Change Set:		1027HighlightingSelFix-srDate:			23 April 2000Author:			Stephan RudlofFix for PluggableListMorph/SimpleHierarchicalListMorph:Highlighting/unhighlighting works correctly now, if colors of StringMorphs are changed programmatically to highlight/unhighlight colors of PluggableListMorph and SimpleHierarchicalListMorph."!!PluggableListMorph methodsFor: 'drawing' stamp: 'sr 4/23/2000 01:26'!highlightSelection	selectedMorph ifNotNil: [selectedMorph color: Color red; changed]! !!PluggableListMorph methodsFor: 'drawing' stamp: 'sr 4/23/2000 01:27'!unhighlightSelection	selectedMorph ifNotNil: [selectedMorph color: Color black; changed]! !!SimpleHierarchicalListMorph methodsFor: 'drawing' stamp: 'sr 4/23/2000 01:27'!highlightSelection	selectedMorph ifNotNil: [selectedMorph color: Color red; changed]! !!SimpleHierarchicalListMorph methodsFor: 'drawing' stamp: 'sr 4/23/2000 01:27'!unhighlightSelection	selectedMorph ifNotNil: [selectedMorph color: Color black; changed]! !